This is a high level steps on how to get Jupyter notebook to see the GPUs. This is applicable for the laptop machines which have an Nvidia GPUs. The steps are simple

1. Install WSL on Windows
2. Install conda and create a new environment
3. Install tensor flow within this instance of linux on windows
4. Install jupter, nbextensions
5. All set


PS: https://www.tensorflow.org/install/pip#windows-wsl2
